{"tid":1786001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我見到有個channel冇乜人知","createTime":"2019-12-16T23:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T18:24:50.000Z","uid":289949,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1faac499b513fb7d86cb682ad6d03062b9dd7a","tid":1786001,"uid":289949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T23:38:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/freehkss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehkss&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0q3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=f75f7038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/freehkss</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係幾個能力小但想幫小朋友嘅學生 我地只不過想做一個中介人 渠道去幫有需要嘅人 我見之前都有類似嘅channel 但係大部分都已經停止運作 <br />\n<br />\n呢個channel會幫助有需要嘅手足 我接觸過好多小朋友都因為政見問題 比屋企趕出門口 cut零用錢 冇飯食等等 佢地大多數都會唔出聲 怕麻煩到其他人 但係根本就唔係你地錯 我地香港人欠你地太多 ！<br />\n<br />\n家長同小朋友放心 所有個人資料都會保密 因為我地唔會想知你係邊個❌❌ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有金錢去向都會有足夠透明度比家長去了解 金錢一定去到有需要嘅人手上<br />\n<br />\n我地會Fact check 所有申請人 同會將所有個案記錄底 <br />\n<br />\n家長支援:<br />\n<br />\n我地宜家暫時接收⬇️<br />\n<br />\n飯卷✅<br />\n八達通✅<br />\n文具✅<br />\n住宿支援✅<br />\n生活費✅<br />\n工作職位✅"},{"pid":"7026fe9be49a6700177593325ec7fb012eabd16d","tid":1786001,"uid":289949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T23:39:31.000Z","msg":"之前類似嘅channel 幫過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想佢幫到有需要嘅人"},{"pid":"31ee652487690e571b5451d13040a7b368f290e0","tid":1786001,"uid":102037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T23:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d182ad144db7d5b9e80748625c5e8dc23c5e367","tid":1786001,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T23:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/freehkss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehkss&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0q3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=f75f7038\" target